
Climate change has been a significant issue in our lives in recent years.
Everyone can help limit climate change. We can make a difference from the way we travel to the food we eat and our clothes.
The app provides information about several topics, including the primary and most spoken climate change factors:
Deforestation, fashion, food, automotive, and the bitcoin industries.
The app's goal is to direct you individually on how you can contribute by your daily life actions to reduce pollution on earth.
The app provides a personal questionnaire. It will examine the level of your impact on the environment.
Through this questionnaire, you can find out which topics you should explore more by the recommendations the app will give you.
Press on the 'personal questionnaire' button to continue.

good luck!
